en_12042_0	A valuable lecture on ‘Young age and Woman soldier’ was conducted by Lieutenant Colonel B. G. S Samanthi of National Cadet Corps (NCC) for the benefit of woman recruits under training at Sandunpura Recruit Training Centre for woman soldiers on Thursday (13).
en_12042_1	Organized by the Directorate of Psychological Operations, the lecture covered a wide area of day to day domestic and social issues as well as their personal concerns.
en_12042_2	100 plus troops including Officers attended the lecture.
